WEBVTT

00:01:42.869 --> 00:01:45.305
Come out!
You can't run anymore!

00:01:45.572 --> 00:01:48.608
-We'll shoot!
-Give up already, Abdul Hakim!

00:01:52.846 --> 00:01:54.714
-So, you wanna fight?
-You're such a...

00:02:46.366 --> 00:02:47.534
<i>Amigo!</i>

00:02:47.600 --> 00:02:50.870
<i>How are all you 300,000 bounty hunters</i>
<i>in the solar system doing?</i>

00:02:50.937 --> 00:02:54.574
<i>It's time for </i>Big Shot, <i>the show that</i>
<i>brings you information about fugitives!</i>

00:02:54.641 --> 00:02:59.512
<i>Well, well, first up for today,</i>
<i>is this guy: Abdul Hakim.</i>

00:03:00.480 --> 00:03:03.683
<i>He's known as a serial pet thief.</i>

00:03:03.750 --> 00:03:05.552
<i>This time, he snagged a test animal</i>

00:03:05.618 --> 00:03:07.954
<i>from a research facility,</i>
<i>and is on the loose.</i>

00:03:08.488 --> 00:03:12.425
<i>The good news is that he's</i>
<i>worth a whopping 8 million!</i>

00:03:12.492 --> 00:03:14.260
<i>The conditions are as always.</i>

00:03:14.327 --> 00:03:16.529
<i>Bring him in alive</i>
<i>to collect your reward.</i>

00:03:16.596 --> 00:03:18.865
<i>If you kill him,</i>
<i>kiss your reward goodbye.</i>

00:03:18.932 --> 00:03:22.335
<i>He's the biggest we've had in a while.</i>
<i>Do your best to get this guy.</i>

00:03:22.402 --> 00:03:23.269
How's it look?

00:03:23.603 --> 00:03:24.704
It's done for.

00:03:25.438 --> 00:03:26.973
Man, why does everything...

00:03:29.542 --> 00:03:30.476
<i>Hey.</i>

00:03:30.543 --> 00:03:31.911
Doctor? You got information?

00:03:32.579 --> 00:03:33.913
<i>About Abdul Hakim.</i>

00:03:34.747 --> 00:03:37.317
<i>-I'll take it!</i>
-I'll give a discount. 300.

00:03:37.383 --> 00:03:39.285
I got his post-plastic surgery picture.

00:03:39.352 --> 00:03:40.787
<i>Too much. 20 down.</i>

00:03:41.988 --> 00:03:45.558
All right, 280. On one condition.

00:03:46.259 --> 00:03:48.328
-What's that?
<i>-Sock him one.</i>

00:03:49.229 --> 00:03:53.533
<i>He trampled over me.</i>
<i>If you want, punch him a dozen times.</i>

00:04:17.924 --> 00:04:19.926
I've got the goods.

00:04:20.460 --> 00:04:22.629
This one should be something big.

00:04:23.596 --> 00:04:25.465
Yeah, see you in six hours.

00:04:26.399 --> 00:04:29.335
<i>He had a very conspicuous suitcase.</i>

00:04:29.402 --> 00:04:31.371
That info's included in the deal, right?

00:04:31.704 --> 00:04:32.805
<i>Oh, all right.</i>

00:04:33.539 --> 00:04:36.309
<i>It was something that could</i>
<i>carry a small woman inside.</i>

00:04:36.376 --> 00:04:37.377
Treasure?

00:04:37.443 --> 00:04:38.811
<i>Can't really say.</i>

00:04:39.345 --> 00:04:41.714
<i>The way he handled it,</i>
<i>sure didn't seem that way.</i>

00:04:53.393 --> 00:04:56.829
If you feel lethargic,
have a ginseng beverage.

00:04:56.896 --> 00:04:58.698
You'll last a week with it!

00:04:58.765 --> 00:05:01.668
If you're tired,
have a sugarcane beverage.

00:05:01.734 --> 00:05:04.437
You ate too much?
Then have a pineapple beverage.

00:05:04.504 --> 00:05:05.638
Give me some lao chu.

00:05:05.905 --> 00:05:06.839
Thank you.

00:05:07.573 --> 00:05:08.441
Here you go.

00:05:11.311 --> 00:05:13.946
Sorry. My apologies, bro.

00:05:15.848 --> 00:05:17.884
Hey, I said I'm sorry.

00:05:18.418 --> 00:05:20.420
What, can't say anything?

00:05:23.923 --> 00:05:25.858
What? You picking a fight?

00:05:28.494 --> 00:05:29.595
My treat.

00:05:35.802 --> 00:05:36.669
Drink.

00:06:01.060 --> 00:06:03.596
And now, the loot.

00:06:30.723 --> 00:06:33.493
Even if I overhaul this whole craft,
I'll have some change.

00:06:33.860 --> 00:06:35.695
Guess I'll go eat Peking duck with it.

00:06:36.095 --> 00:06:39.599
As they say,
"Don't count chickens before they hatch."

00:06:41.534 --> 00:06:42.902
I got this one nailed shut.

00:06:42.969 --> 00:06:44.470
<i>Well, give it what you got.</i>

00:06:53.780 --> 00:06:55.047
So, all three went down?

00:06:55.815 --> 00:06:56.682
Seems that way.

00:06:57.016 --> 00:06:58.651
And Hakim is around here?

00:06:58.951 --> 00:06:59.952
Seems that way.

00:07:00.553 --> 00:07:02.922
He doesn't even know
how much that thing is worth.

00:07:03.656 --> 00:07:05.091
A pet shop?

00:07:05.892 --> 00:07:07.426
A shady one at that.

00:07:07.927 --> 00:07:12.865
Hey, bro, you can buy
anything here on Mars.

00:07:13.499 --> 00:07:16.502
From guns to human lives.

00:07:16.702 --> 00:07:18.971
If you wanna know,
show me what you got.

00:07:19.038 --> 00:07:22.208
The chain on this one is long.
Must be <i>The</i> <i>Way of the Dragon </i>model.

00:07:22.809 --> 00:07:26.112
Oh, you can tell?
That's a rare one from the '30s!

00:07:27.547 --> 00:07:29.015
It sure is an antique.

00:07:30.082 --> 00:07:34.086
Try the store called Animal Treasure
off of Caiphon Road.

00:07:34.854 --> 00:07:36.622
I'm sure you'll find something there.

00:07:42.061 --> 00:07:46.032
Okay, I'll look, but I'll decide if I
want to buy it from you after I see it.

00:07:46.098 --> 00:07:47.166
Oh, all right.

00:08:00.746 --> 00:08:04.016
Run out of funds changing your
face around too much, Hakim?

00:08:04.083 --> 00:08:05.518
Wait a sec.

00:08:05.585 --> 00:08:06.953
Hey, don't move.

00:08:07.019 --> 00:08:10.556
You sure are restless,
changing your face around this much.

00:08:10.623 --> 00:08:11.491
What the...?

00:08:11.557 --> 00:08:14.527
Hold it. I don't want any
of this business here.

00:08:14.594 --> 00:08:16.262
All of my babies are very sensitive.

00:08:16.529 --> 00:08:17.597
You open it.

00:08:18.097 --> 00:08:19.799
Why do I?

00:08:19.866 --> 00:08:21.868
-There seems to be some sort of--
-Hurry up!

00:08:26.973 --> 00:08:28.040
Oh, fine.

00:08:44.557 --> 00:08:45.224
A dog?

00:08:45.291 --> 00:08:48.895
A Welsh Corgi.
It's cute, but it's everywhere.

00:08:48.961 --> 00:08:51.063
Not a particularly rare species.

00:08:51.531 --> 00:08:53.566
And how much is it worth?

00:08:53.933 --> 00:08:56.536
With the suitcase, about this much.

00:08:56.602 --> 00:08:58.638
-200K?
-No, no, 200, 200!

00:08:58.704 --> 00:08:59.739
No way!

00:08:59.972 --> 00:09:03.175
You don't like it, you take care
of it yourself. Like eating it.

00:09:03.242 --> 00:09:04.310
It is a puppy.

00:09:05.077 --> 00:09:07.747
Sorry to bother you. Please continue.

00:09:16.155 --> 00:09:18.157
I guess the Peking duck
has been overcooked.

00:09:18.858 --> 00:09:20.226
At least give me 300.

00:09:20.293 --> 00:09:21.327
No can do.

00:09:21.594 --> 00:09:23.229
-280?
-A no is a no.

00:09:23.863 --> 00:09:24.864
250!

00:09:24.931 --> 00:09:26.999
Zero. I'll take it back.

00:09:27.733 --> 00:09:29.802
This again?
What is it this time?

00:09:39.045 --> 00:09:41.847
Someone! Catch my babies! Hurry!

00:09:42.148 --> 00:09:43.249
-There it is!
-All right!

00:09:50.022 --> 00:09:53.125
Hakim?
Goddamn it, what's going on?

00:10:35.134 --> 00:10:36.335
-Gangway!
-What the hell?

00:10:37.069 --> 00:10:38.638
Wait, damn it!

00:10:38.871 --> 00:10:40.339
Hey, what the hell do you want?

00:10:54.987 --> 00:10:56.255
Bounty hunter?

00:10:56.756 --> 00:10:58.124
Animal rights syndicate?

00:10:58.791 --> 00:11:00.693
Your story brings a tear to my eye.

00:11:00.760 --> 00:11:03.162
Risking your life on a dog
that's worth 200 woolongs.

00:11:03.229 --> 00:11:04.230
What?

00:11:04.697 --> 00:11:09.335
What I want are the 8 million woolongs
hanging from your neck.

00:11:21.447 --> 00:11:22.815
Not bad.

00:11:24.250 --> 00:11:25.351
What?

00:11:25.885 --> 00:11:26.852
Damn it!

00:11:42.201 --> 00:11:44.970
Shut up!
I'm in a rotten mood right now!

00:11:58.984 --> 00:12:01.854
There, there.
Here, let me put on a collar.

00:12:03.022 --> 00:12:05.124
A dog instead of a duck, huh?

00:12:05.191 --> 00:12:07.927
Forget about that.
You know anything about it?

00:12:07.993 --> 00:12:12.431
Yeah. This is a Welsh Corgi.
A total mongrel.

00:12:13.032 --> 00:12:16.902
-Totally?
-Totally. Completely worthless.

00:12:17.236 --> 00:12:19.905
Shit, this gives me a headache.

00:12:20.172 --> 00:12:22.308
And all this
is because of this mongrel--

00:12:25.311 --> 00:12:29.181
The dog is worthless,
but the owner is worth something.

00:12:29.248 --> 00:12:32.118
Well, at least you should
get to know this critter well.

00:12:33.119 --> 00:12:34.887
Man, I hate kids and critters!

00:12:35.354 --> 00:12:37.289
They're nothing but trouble.

00:12:40.259 --> 00:12:41.327
I got something!

00:12:41.393 --> 00:12:42.428
All right!

00:12:42.995 --> 00:12:44.363
-It's big!
-Here it comes!

00:12:44.430 --> 00:12:45.931
Pull on the line!

00:12:51.237 --> 00:12:52.304
What time is it now?

00:12:55.141 --> 00:12:56.242
It's four o'clock now.

00:12:57.309 --> 00:12:58.844
Two hours.

00:13:01.847 --> 00:13:04.383
Who was that with Hakim? His ally?

00:13:04.450 --> 00:13:05.451
Seems that way.

00:13:05.518 --> 00:13:08.854
We got no clues?
We have to do something.

00:13:08.921 --> 00:13:11.290
If that falls into police hands,
we're in deep shit.

00:13:11.557 --> 00:13:12.424
Seems that way.

00:13:13.025 --> 00:13:16.462
All our work will be worthless if our
experiments get revealed to the public.

00:13:16.529 --> 00:13:17.563
Seems that way.

00:13:17.830 --> 00:13:20.799
How much does he think
we put into that "data dog"?

00:13:21.901 --> 00:13:23.836
Why don't you do this?

00:13:23.903 --> 00:13:28.841
Didn't your grandma teach you
to finish what you start?

00:13:29.108 --> 00:13:30.943
She was dead before I was born.

00:13:31.343 --> 00:13:35.381
<i>Sorry to hear that.</i>
<i>Anyway, we have the joker in our hand.</i>

00:13:36.115 --> 00:13:38.017
Just do what we planned.

00:13:38.484 --> 00:13:40.519
Give me code name "snoop."

00:13:42.388 --> 00:13:45.491
Yeah. It's me.
I had some trouble.

00:13:47.259 --> 00:13:49.161
No big deal.

00:13:50.129 --> 00:13:51.864
Hey, wait, Michael!

00:13:53.399 --> 00:13:55.834
I want to postpone the meeting a bit.

00:13:56.602 --> 00:13:58.404
As I said, it wasn't that big a deal.

00:13:59.505 --> 00:14:02.007
Impossible? Why? Hey, wait!

00:14:10.416 --> 00:14:12.284
And this is our plan?

00:14:16.989 --> 00:14:18.490
Hey, you!

00:14:19.091 --> 00:14:21.493
You have something
you want to know, right?

00:14:22.194 --> 00:14:23.929
Wait!

00:14:23.996 --> 00:14:27.499
My little Peeko
can answer your questions!

00:14:28.634 --> 00:14:31.470
You have something
you want to know, right?

00:14:32.104 --> 00:14:35.074
See, little Peeko is telling me

00:14:35.140 --> 00:14:39.078
that you're looking
for someone or something.

00:14:43.382 --> 00:14:47.486
Well, where there's this dog,
there's Hakim.

00:14:48.387 --> 00:14:49.922
Seeing loud and clear.

00:14:50.522 --> 00:14:53.025
We're counting on you, pooch.

00:14:54.059 --> 00:14:56.462
We must resort to the dog whistle.

00:14:56.528 --> 00:14:58.497
But that'll cause a big mess.

00:14:58.931 --> 00:15:01.166
-I don't care.
-We'll draw attention to ourselves.

00:15:01.233 --> 00:15:03.636
-We have no choice.
-Shall I?

00:15:03.903 --> 00:15:04.670
Do it.

00:15:13.512 --> 00:15:14.680
I can't hear anything.

00:15:15.147 --> 00:15:17.316
I said before that humans can't hear it.

00:15:17.616 --> 00:15:19.318
Oh, that's right.

00:15:20.019 --> 00:15:22.688
This is so farfetched.

00:15:24.023 --> 00:15:26.525
Will this really attract?

00:15:32.498 --> 00:15:35.501
Oh, it's moving.
Something is now on the move.

00:15:38.103 --> 00:15:41.173
Wait!
Babies, what's wrong with you guys?

00:15:44.143 --> 00:15:45.210
Hey, wait!

00:15:50.683 --> 00:15:52.251
It got away, Jet!

00:15:53.352 --> 00:15:55.220
-Hakim?
<i>-No, the dog!</i>

00:15:55.287 --> 00:15:59.625
It's close, it's close.
What you are looking for is nearby.

00:16:00.159 --> 00:16:03.062
In fact, right in front of your eyes.

00:16:05.197 --> 00:16:06.732
Hey, wait, you need to pay!

00:16:06.999 --> 00:16:09.601
-I'll pay when I am rich.
-You can't be serious.

00:16:17.309 --> 00:16:19.545
Goddamn it, what the hell is going on?

00:16:25.584 --> 00:16:26.986
Happy?

00:16:27.052 --> 00:16:28.420
Yes, very.

00:16:31.090 --> 00:16:32.524
-Excuse me.
-Out of my way.

00:16:36.595 --> 00:16:38.731
You, what are you doing?

00:16:42.668 --> 00:16:43.669
Hakim!

00:16:51.643 --> 00:16:52.544
Damn it!

00:16:54.646 --> 00:16:56.215
It's just a dog, after all.

00:17:02.354 --> 00:17:03.422
Hakim!

00:17:04.490 --> 00:17:07.226
<i>Spike, he's headed for Interstate 6.</i>

00:17:07.726 --> 00:17:11.130
<i>Great. If he thinks he can outrun me,</i>
<i>he's welcome to try.</i>

00:17:11.196 --> 00:17:12.664
Don't get too hotheaded.

00:17:13.132 --> 00:17:14.800
What part of me is hotheaded?

00:17:19.705 --> 00:17:20.606
There he is.

00:17:38.257 --> 00:17:39.591
This is payback from earlier!

00:17:48.500 --> 00:17:51.236
The hell are you doing?
This guy is mine!

00:18:00.379 --> 00:18:02.147
-What the--?
-Now!

00:18:05.451 --> 00:18:06.518
Stop that!

00:18:08.153 --> 00:18:09.354
Shit.

00:18:12.391 --> 00:18:13.258
Shit!

00:18:13.659 --> 00:18:15.794
This is why I hate critters!

00:18:37.583 --> 00:18:38.884
<i>Amigo!</i>

00:18:39.151 --> 00:18:42.387
<i>How are all you 300,000 bounty hunters</i>
<i>in the solar system doing?</i>

00:18:42.454 --> 00:18:46.458
<i>It's time for </i>Big Shot, <i>the show that</i>
<i>brings you information about fugitives!</i>

00:18:46.525 --> 00:18:48.861
<i>So, you remember Abdul Hakim</i>
<i>who chose a rather</i>

00:18:49.128 --> 00:18:51.830
<i>flashy way</i>
<i>of turning himself in last week?</i>

00:18:51.897 --> 00:18:53.532
<i>Yeah! Of course!</i>

00:18:53.599 --> 00:18:57.169
<i>Apparently, he stole</i>
<i>what's called a "data dog"</i>

00:18:57.236 --> 00:19:00.839
<i>created in an illegal experiment</i>
<i>of some research firm.</i>

00:19:01.707 --> 00:19:02.641
<i>What's that?</i>

00:19:02.708 --> 00:19:07.646
<i>I'm not sure myself, but apparently,</i>
<i>it's a very intelligent pooch.</i>

00:19:07.713 --> 00:19:11.450
<i>I hear that it's priceless</i>
<i>among collectors.</i>

00:19:11.517 --> 00:19:16.355
<i>That's a surprise!</i>
<i>I wanna have a dog like that!</i>

00:19:16.421 --> 00:19:18.724
<i>But they say it's still missing.</i>

00:19:18.790 --> 00:19:20.826
<i>I wonder where it went.</i>

00:19:20.893 --> 00:19:23.896
<i>Really. But now, a commercial!</i>

00:19:26.298 --> 00:19:27.566
Can't be.

00:19:27.900 --> 00:19:32.371
Hey, there. When you're done cleaning,
feed the komodo dragons.

00:19:32.938 --> 00:19:34.940
I want you to work your ass off!

00:19:35.207 --> 00:19:35.941
Yeah.

00:19:38.677 --> 00:19:39.778
Hey, hey.

00:19:43.248 --> 00:19:45.184
Hey, don't jump on there.

00:19:46.185 --> 00:19:46.852
That's cold!

00:19:48.654 --> 00:19:51.690
That's why I said we should
throw out mongrels like this one.

00:19:51.757 --> 00:19:53.659
But you're the one
that brought it here.

00:19:54.526 --> 00:19:56.929
In any case, we have to do
something about the ticks.

00:19:57.696 --> 00:20:01.333
Shit. I'm gonna salt you
and eat you, damn it.

00:20:01.867 --> 00:20:04.203
<i>Well, it's time for us to go.</i>
<i>See you next time!</i>

00:20:04.269 --> 00:20:05.404
<i>Good luck!</i>

00:21:47.406 --> 00:21:50.075
<i>"Nothing is permanent."</i>
<i>It's a fact of life.</i>

00:21:51.576 --> 00:21:54.046
<i>The bell tolls for the great ones</i>
<i>who will someday fall.</i>

00:21:54.313 --> 00:21:56.348
<i>Money makes the world go round,</i>

00:21:57.316 --> 00:21:59.851
<i>but debt piles up</i>
<i>before you know it.</i>

00:22:00.986 --> 00:22:03.522
<i>I wandered through</i>
<i>all the reaches of space</i>

00:22:03.855 --> 00:22:05.924
<i>and there I met a cowboy.</i>

00:22:06.792 --> 00:22:10.996
<i>A session to the tune</i>
<i>of an off-key melody:</i>

00:22:11.530 --> 00:22:12.998
<i>"Honky Tonk Women."</i>

